<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><head><link href="/site_media/static/css/book.css" rel="stylesheet"/></head><body><div class="role-section1" data-chtitle="سورة الشرح" id="ch94"><h1 id="70.x7WYn">سورة الشرح</h1><div class="surah_tafsir"><div class="verse-tafsir" data-verse="94:1"><span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v" id="qr-aljalalain-94-1">أَلَمْ نَشْرَحْ لَكَ صَدْرَكَ</span><a class="vn" href="/quran/94/1" target="_blank" title="سورة الشرح" data-v="94:1"></a><span class="ve">﴾</span></span><div class="tafsir"><p id="70.OPpKx"/><p id="70.ndPnX"><span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v">أَلَمْ نَشْرَحْ</span><span class="ve">﴾</span></span> استفهام تقرير أي شرحنا <span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v">لَكَ</span><span class="ve">﴾</span></span> يا محمد <span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v">صَدْرَكَ</span><span class="ve">﴾</span></span> بالنبوّة وغيرها؟.</p><p id="70.Zq2aD"/></div></div><div class="verse-tafsir" data-verse="94:2"><span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v" id="qr-aljalalain-94-2">وَوَضَعْنَا عَنْكَ وِزْرَكَ</span><a class="vn" href="/quran/94/2" target="_blank" title="سورة الشرح" data-v="94:2"></a><span class="ve">﴾</span></span><div class="tafsir"><p id="70.Xgn4Z"/><p id="70.V5nzA"><span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v">وَوَضَعْنَا</span><span class="ve">﴾</span></span> حططنا <span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v">عَنكَ وِزْرَكَ</span><span class="ve">﴾</span></span>.</p><p id="70.93M8R"/></div></div><div class="verse-tafsir" data-verse="94:3"><span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v" id="qr-aljalalain-94-3">الَّذِي أَنْقَضَ ظَهْرَكَ</span><a class="vn" href="/quran/94/3" target="_blank" title="سورة الشرح" data-v="94:3"></a><span class="ve">﴾</span></span><div class="tafsir"><p id="70.59nxe"/><p id="70.6X9Z5"><span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v">الذي أَنقَضَ</span><span class="ve">﴾</span></span> أثقل <span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v">ظَهْرَكَ</span><span class="ve">﴾</span></span> وهذا كقوله تعالى: <span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v">لِّيَغْفِرَ لَكَ الله مَا تَقَدَّمَ مِن ذَنبِكَ</span><span class="ve">﴾</span></span> .</p><p id="70.ApV42"/></div></div><div class="verse-tafsir" data-verse="94:4"><span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v" id="qr-aljalalain-94-4">وَرَفَعْنَا لَكَ ذِكْرَكَ</span><a class="vn" href="/quran/94/4" target="_blank" title="سورة الشرح" data-v="94:4"></a><span class="ve">﴾</span></span><div class="tafsir"><p id="70.z7L4r"/><p id="70.dYqp3"><span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v">وَرَفَعْنَا لَكَ ذِكْرَكَ</span><span class="ve">﴾</span></span> بأن تُذكر مع ذكري في الأذان والإِقامة والتشهد والخطبة وغيرها.</p><p id="70.dR6pj"/></div></div><div class="verse-tafsir" data-verse="94:5"><span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v" id="qr-aljalalain-94-5">فَإِنَّ مَعَ الْعُسْرِ يُسْرًا</span><a class="vn" href="/quran/94/5" target="_blank" title="سورة الشرح" data-v="94:5"></a><span class="ve">﴾</span></span><div class="tafsir"><p id="70.6Ylz4"/><p id="70.6pV9N"><span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v">فَإِنَّ مَعَ العسر</span><span class="ve">﴾</span></span> الشدّة <span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v">يُسْراً</span><span class="ve">﴾</span></span> سهولة.</p><p id="70.J71Vb"/></div></div><div class="verse-tafsir" data-verse="94:6"><span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v" id="qr-aljalalain-94-6">إِنَّ مَعَ الْعُسْرِ يُسْرًا</span><a class="vn" href="/quran/94/6" target="_blank" title="سورة الشرح" data-v="94:6"></a><span class="ve">﴾</span></span><div class="tafsir"><p id="70.DVDW7"/><p id="70.G6leA"><span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v">إِنَّ مَعَ العسر يُسْراً</span><span class="ve">﴾</span></span> والنبي صلى الله عليه وسلم قاسى من الكفار شدّة، ثم حصل له اليسر بنصره عليهم.</p><p id="70.MNa9D"/></div></div><div class="verse-tafsir" data-verse="94:7"><span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v" id="qr-aljalalain-94-7">فَإِذَا فَرَغْتَ فَانْصَبْ</span><a class="vn" href="/quran/94/7" target="_blank" title="سورة الشرح" data-v="94:7"></a><span class="ve">﴾</span></span><div class="tafsir"><p id="70.Y10DA"/><p id="70.2RWZz"><span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v">فَإِذَا فَرَغْتَ</span><span class="ve">﴾</span></span> من الصلاة <span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v">فانصب</span><span class="ve">﴾</span></span> اتعب في الدعاء.</p><p id="70.MPokA"/></div></div><div class="verse-tafsir" data-verse="94:8"><span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v" id="qr-aljalalain-94-8">وَإِلَى رَبِّكَ فَارْغَبْ</span><a class="vn" href="/quran/94/8" target="_blank" title="سورة الشرح" data-v="94:8"></a><span class="ve">﴾</span></span><div class="tafsir"><p id="70.r5zMX"/><p id="70.ZVM9d"><span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v">وإلى رَبِّكَ فارغب</span><span class="ve">﴾</span></span> تضرع.</p><p id="70.rYG4b"/></div></div></div></div></body></html>